<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type">
</head>
<body>

<p>A PSAP user has requested to change institutions:</p>

<dl>
  <dt>First Name</dt>
  <dd><%= @user.first_name %></dd>
  <dt>Last Name</dt>
  <dd><%= @user.last_name %></dd>
  <dt>Username</dt>
  <dd><%= @user.username %></dd>
  <dt>Email</dt>
  <dd><%= @user.email %></dd>
</dl>

<% if @user.institution %>
  <p>The user's current institution is: <strong><%= @user.institution.name %></strong>.</p>
  <p>He/she wishes to move to
    <strong><%= @user.desired_institution.name %></strong>.</p>
<% else %>
  <p>The user wishes to join
    <strong><%= @user.desired_institution.name %></strong>.</p>
<% end %>

<ol>
  <li>If this request seems legitimate, please
    <%= link_to('sign in to the PSAP and approve the user\'s request', @user_url) %> at
    your earliest convenience.</li>
  <li>If you are not sure, please
    <%= link_to('send the user an email', 'mailto:' + @user.email) %>
    requesting more information.</li>
</ol>

</body>
</html>
